<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4653286>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Reproductive anatomy of Austrochloritis speculoris. (A–B) Drawings showing the entire reproductive system:(A)AM C.575464 (NSW, Point Lookout); (B) AM C.575456 (NSW, Ebor–Guyra Rd). (D–F) Details of penial anatomy: (C) AM C.575464 (NSW, Point Lookout); (D) AM C.575456 (NSW, Ebor–Guyra Rd). Scale bars = 5 mm. Abbreviations: ag—albumen gland; at—atrium; bc—bursa copulatirx; ep—epiphallus; fl—epiphallic flagellum; hd—hermaphroditic duct; ipw—inner penial wall; p—penis; pm—penial retractor; pv—penial verge; va—vagina; vd—vas deferens." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4653286/files/figure.png" .

